name: Bounce House Rental
short_description: Inflatable Rentals in New City NY for Every Occasion! Bounce N Jump Party Rentals is known as a family-owned and operated party rental business. We center on providing safe and quality party rental equipment that is clean and sanitized with on time delivery and the best customer care available! Book your bouncer today and we guarantee it will make your next event even better!! * Inflatables for birthday parties, corporate events, fundraisers and more! * Prices include FREE delivery, setup and removal.  * We are fully insured, registered and examined by the state of New york
